@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@adminUsername = admin
@ownerUsername = li_ming
@employeeUsername = chen_xu
@password = 123456
@repeatableAdminReorderProjectName = reorder_node_admin_case_{{$timestamp}}
@repeatableOwnerReorderProjectName = reorder_node_owner_case_{{$timestamp}}
@repeatablePersonalReorderProjectName = reorder_node_personal_case_{{$timestamp}}
@projectWithCompletedNodeId = 1
@completedNodeId = 1
@completedProjectId = 3
@completedProjectNodeId = 3
@missingProjectId = 999999
@missingNodeId = 999999
@invalidProjectId = 0

### 提示：正常路径会先创建临时项目和多个阶段节点，再执行重排，因此可以重复回放。
### 提示：固定使用 project 1 / node 1 验证“项目未完成但已存在完成节点，不允许重排”；固定使用 project 3 / node 3 验证“项目已完成，不允许重排”。

### 正常路径：管理员登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 正常路径：管理员创建临时项目
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectName}}",
  "description": "用于验证管理员调整阶段节点顺序接口。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-01",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-30"
}

> {% client.global.set("repeatableAdminReorderProjectId", response.body.data.id); %}

### 正常路径：管理员创建第一个阶段节点
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectId}}/nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "需求梳理",
  "description": "用于重排测试的第一个节点。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-02",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-05"
}

> {% client.global.set("repeatableAdminReorderNodeId1", response.body.data.id); %}

### 正常路径：管理员创建第二个阶段节点
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectId}}/nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "原型设计",
  "description": "用于重排测试的第二个节点。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-06",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-10"
}

> {% client.global.set("repeatableAdminReorderNodeId2", response.body.data.id); %}

### 正常路径：管理员创建第三个阶段节点
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectId}}/nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "开发实现",
  "description": "用于重排测试的第三个节点。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-11",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-18"
}

> {% client.global.set("repeatableAdminReorderNodeId3", response.body.data.id); %}

### 正常路径：管理员调整临时项目的阶段节点顺序
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId3}},
      "sequence_no": 1
    },
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId1}},
      "sequence_no": 2
    },
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId2}},
      "sequence_no": 3
    }
  ]
}

### 正常路径：管理员获取阶段节点列表，确认顺序已持久化
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectId}}/nodes

### 正常路径：管理员登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：未登录调整阶段节点顺序，预期 401
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId1}},
      "sequence_no": 1
    },
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId2}},
      "sequence_no": 2
    },
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId3}},
      "sequence_no": 3
    }
  ]
}

