### 异常路径：普通员工调整非本人负责项目下的阶段节点顺序，预期 403
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId1}},
      "sequence_no": 1
    },
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId2}},
      "sequence_no": 2
    },
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId3}},
      "sequence_no": 3
    }
  ]
}

### 正常路径：普通员工登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：重新登录管理员
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：管理员调整普通员工个人自用项目的阶段节点顺序，预期 403
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatablePersonalReorderProjectId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatablePersonalReorderNodeId1}},
      "sequence_no": 1
    },
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatablePersonalReorderNodeId2}},
      "sequence_no": 2
    }
  ]
}

### 异常路径：project_id 小于等于 0，预期 400
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{invalidProjectId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "node_id": 1,
      "sequence_no": 1
    }
  ]
}

### 异常路径：请求体不是 JSON 对象，预期 400
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId1}},
    "sequence_no": 1
  }
]

### 异常路径：缺少 nodes，预期 400
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：nodes 不是数组，预期 400
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodes": {}
}

### 异常路径：nodes 为空数组，预期 400
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodes": []
}

### 异常路径：nodes 中元素不是对象，预期 400
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodes": [
    1
  ]
}

### 异常路径：nodes[].node_id 不是整数，预期 400
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "node_id": "1",
      "sequence_no": 1
    }
  ]
}

### 异常路径：nodes[].sequence_no 不是整数，预期 400
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId1}},
      "sequence_no": "1"
    }
  ]
}

### 异常路径：nodes[].node_id 重复，预期 400
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId1}},
      "sequence_no": 1
    },
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId1}},
      "sequence_no": 2
    }
  ]
}

### 异常路径：nodes[].sequence_no 重复，预期 400
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId1}},
      "sequence_no": 1
    },
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId2}},
      "sequence_no": 1
    }
  ]
}

### 异常路径：nodes[].sequence_no 不是从 1 连续递增，预期 400
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId1}},
      "sequence_no": 2
    },
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId2}},
      "sequence_no": 3
    }
  ]
}

### 异常路径：请求节点中存在不存在的阶段节点，预期 404
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId1}},
      "sequence_no": 1
    },
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId2}},
      "sequence_no": 2
    },
    {
      "node_id": {{missingNodeId}},
      "sequence_no": 3
    }
  ]
}

### 异常路径：提交的不是完整节点集合，预期 409
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminReorderProjectId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId1}},
      "sequence_no": 1
    },
    {
      "node_id": {{repeatableAdminReorderNodeId2}},
      "sequence_no": 2
    }
  ]
}

### 异常路径：项目已存在已完成节点，预期 409
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectWithCompletedNodeId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "node_id": {{completedNodeId}},
      "sequence_no": 1
    }
  ]
}

### 异常路径：项目已完成，不允许调整节点顺序，预期 409
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{completedProjectId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "node_id": {{completedProjectNodeId}},
      "sequence_no": 1
    }
  ]
}

### 异常路径：项目不存在，预期 404
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{missingProjectId}}/nodes/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "node_id": {{missingNodeId}},
      "sequence_no": 1
    }
  ]
}
